                <div class="about-section about-section-1">
                    <p>
                        During my MBA studies, when the world spoke in spreadsheets and strategies, <strong>the flute chose me</strong>—or perhaps I finally heard its call. As my Guru says, <strong>"The flute chooses its musician when the musician is ready to listen."</strong> 
